  "text": "This mobility research faces some significant challenges: First, these check-in sources do not usually contain very much ancillary categorical information about a trip such as mode, weather, purpose, number of passengers, etc. Thus, if one wants to know the effect of external factors, one may be limited by resources to determine all of them accurately [CITATION_1] .",
